summary:
- **Index Methodology Change**: The Markit iBoxx Global Developed Markets Liquid High Yield Capped Index (AUD Hedged) will remove the 10% cap on Rule 144A TRACE-Eligible bonds, effective **1 August 2025**.  
- **Impacted ETF**: iShares Global High Yield Bond (AUD Hedged) ETF (**ASX:IHHY**) will reflect this change in its benchmark index.  
- **Expanded Universe**: Post-change, the index will gradually include more TRACE-Eligible 144A bonds.  
- **PDS Update**: A revised Product Disclosure Statement will be issued on the effective date.  

**No material trading or capital markets impact identified for other listed ETFs (IHCB, IHEB, AESG, IUSG, ULTB).**
